# coc-csharp-ls

csharp-ls exension for coc.nvim

## Install

`:CocInstall coc-csharp-ls`

## Keymaps

`nmap <silent> <C-l> <Plug>(coc-coc-csharp-ls-keymap)`

## Lists

`:CocList demo_list`
